I told you to let me go.

153
00:16:07,447 --> 00:16:08,597
Don’t do this.

154
00:16:18,667 --> 00:16:20,577
How did you get into my room?

155
00:16:20,577 --> 00:16:22,087
What you’re doing isn’t right.

156
00:16:23,087 --> 00:16:24,797
Release me.
I won’t

157
