159
00:16:36,847 --> 00:16:37,937
Can you let me go now?

160
00:16:39,337 --> 00:16:41,957
Isn’t this the man who helped me when I fell from the tree?

161
00:16:44,247 --> 00:16:47,357
If I let you go, don’t do anything to me, okay?

162
00:16:48,377 --> 00:16:49,157
Okay.

163
00:16:55,027 --> 00:16:58,287
Hey, what are you doing with me? You crazy bastard!

164
00:16:58,777 --> 00:17:00,777
You psycho!

165
00:17:01,577 --> 00:17:02,557
I’m sorry.

166
00:17:03,687 --> 00:17:04,937
