Huh?

194
00:19:55,087 --> 00:19:57,737
Found who? Don't tell me…

195
00:19:58,087 --> 00:19:58,667
Yes.

196
00:19:59,537 --> 00:20:01,247
How could you be so sure it's him?

197
00:20:01,687 --> 00:20:04,267
By the smell. I remember his scent.

198
00:20:11,337 --> 00:20:13,487
You have his number, right?

199
00:20:34,537 --> 00:20:35,467
Ob-aun.

200
00:20:36,997 --> 00:20:37,757
Sis.

201
00:20:38,667 --> 00:20:42,177
