205
00:20:53,577 --> 00:20:55,647
You might not be cut out for this job.

206
00:20:56,867 --> 00:20:57,647
Sis.
Come on.

207
00:20:57,907 --> 00:21:00,537
Find something more suited to you.

208
00:21:00,537 --> 00:21:02,267
No, sis. I apologize.

209
00:21:03,907 --> 00:21:06,627
Give me back the shop phone and car key.

210
00:21:07,777 --> 00:21:09,107
Please, I'm really sorry.

211
00:21:09,107 --> 00:21:11,487
Ob-aun, am I a joke to you?

212
00:21:12,027 --> 00:21:13,227
Give them back.

213
00:21:31,137 --> 00:21:33,227
What a shame. Look what I got from lending a hand.

214
00:21:45,777 --> 00:21:48,357
You guys too, I don't want another incident like this.

215
00:22:08,887 --> 00:22:11,247
Ob-aun, you’re in trouble.

216
00:22:11,247 --> 00:22:13,667
Did you copy the work of the godly writer Shi Er Ye?

217
00:22:14,627 --> 00:22:16,997
Readers are furious.

218
00:22:34,197 --> 00:22:36,997
(Shui)

219
00:22:38,087 --> 00:22:40,647
Hey, Little Prince.

220
00:22:41,027 --> 00:22:44,847
You're in big trouble for copying work this time.

221
00:22:44,847 --> 00:22:46,227
But I didn't copy.

222
00:22:47,627 --> 00:22:50,937
Then you need to find evidence. Or else…

223
00:22:52,247 --> 00:22:53,397
Or what?

224
00:22:54,427 --> 00:22:56,537
You'll get sued and banned.

225
00:22:59,197 --> 00:23:01,937
How can I find evidence if I didn't copy?

226
00:23:02,757 --> 00:23:06,467
Alright, I'll see what I can do. That's it for now.

227
00:23:34,687 --> 00:23:38,267
Have you been kicked out of the shop, Little Prince?

228
00:23:38,867 --> 00:23:39,827
Who are you?

229
00:23:41,937 --> 00:23:50,047
I'm just calling to advise you that if you can't write, then don't write.

230
00:23:50,307 --> 00:23:51,707
Get out of the industry.

231
00:23:53,397 --> 00:23:57,867
And one more thing, prepare to be sued.

232
00:24:23,357 --> 00:24:25,247
Hello, the shop is closed.

233
00:24:26,047 --> 00:24:26,797
Hello.

234
00:24:27,537 --> 00:24:30,937
I'd like to ask about the person who delivered food to Condo 85 today.

235
00:24:33,907 --> 00:24:34,847
Um...

236
00:24:36,157 --> 00:24:37,827
Is there a problem with the order?

237
00:24:38,507 --> 00:24:40,157
Oh, no.

238
00:24:40,797 --> 00:24:44,757
I just want a way to contact him. Is that possible?

239
00:24:47,027 --> 00:24:48,337
You mean Ob-aun?

240
00:24:48,597 --> 00:24:50,487
I just kicked him out a moment ago.

241
00:24:50,777 --> 00:24:56,597
But I have to apologize to you. Our policy doesn't allow staff phone numbers.

242
00:24:56,597 --> 00:24:58,597
Even though he's already left.

243
00:24:59,507 --> 00:25:00,937
I'm sorry, sir.

244
00:25:01,937 --> 00:25:03,307
Oh, okay.

245
00:25:04,507 --> 00:25:05,507
Thank you.

246
00:25:26,267 --> 00:25:27,397
I didn't copy anything.

247
00:25:27,647 --> 00:25:29,537
Uh, I know you didn't.

248
00:25:31,997 --> 00:25:34,267
Cut the crap. Why'd you call?

249
00:25:34,827 --> 00:25:39,287
I wanna tell you that I found out where that Shi Er Ye guy lives.

250
00:25:39,507 --> 00:25:42,427
Why don't you go see him? Maybe you can work something out.

251
00:25:42,597 --> 00:25:45,337
Why should I? I didn't copy anything.

252
00:25:47,267 --> 00:25:50,557
It’s up to you. I believe you no matter what.

253
00:25:51,287 --> 00:25:54,087
But readers and people online don’t know you like I do.

254
00:25:54,307 --> 00:25:56,427
Well, you will need to go see him ASAP.

255
00:25:56,427 --> 00:25:58,757
I heard he’s leaving Bangkok tomorrow.

256
00:25:59,707 --> 00:26:01,337
Did you get this info from Khun Pai?

257
00:26:01,427 --> 00:26:04,067
Don’t mind me. I’ll send you the location.

258
00:26:04,707 --> 00:26:05,847
Alright.

259
00:26:09,557 --> 00:26:12,067
Room 1510, Condo 85.

260
00:26:15,177 --> 00:26:18,067
Hey, what are you doing!?
What you’re doing isn’t right.

261
00:26:19,287 --> 00:26:20,957
What are you doing with me? You psycho!

262
00:26:20,957 --> 00:26:24,177
I’m sorry... I didn’t mean to.

263
00:26:24,537 --> 00:26:26,627
Can you... not go anywhere?

264
00:26:30,827 --> 00:26:33,157
Damn, the world is small.

265
00:26:38,887 --> 00:26:42,597
Hey, you don’t need to go find Shi Er Ye right now. Just go meet him in Chiang Mai.

266
00:26:43,337 --> 00:26:45,937
